
# Smart Notes Organizer


## Features
- Add, edit, delete, and search notes
- AI-powered automatic categorization & summarization
- Sentiment analysis

## Tech Stack
- Next.js, TailwindCSS (Frontend)
- Node.js, Express, MongoDB (Backend)
- Jest, Cypress (Testing)
- Deployed on Vercel (FE) & Render (BE)

## Installation
1. `npm install`
2. `npm run dev`


